dialogue: Who wants to see a picture of my new boat?
If we consider the fact that we work much harder than he does...
And we have valuable engineering skills, whereas he can't operate the GPS in his SUV...
And for some reason we don't get paid enough to buy impressive boats.
And we have no nautical interests whatsoever.
I think your best bet is people who don't know you.
This only works if we don't get too familiar.
